{"tid":758398,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"7人進食銅鑼灣外賣奄列鰻魚後疑食物中毒　食肆稱當日曾有外賣服務公司訂餐","createTime":"2018-07-27T15:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T02:55:09.000Z","uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9fc5d2e56b3931d37648c6daa6b3bdce451770","tid":758398,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心今日（27日）公布，指正調查兩宗懷疑食物中毒個案。3名女子及2男2女，上周五（20日）分別進食銅鑼灣一食肆的外賣食物，7人其後均出現發燒、腹痛、腹瀉和嘔吐等病徵，懷疑為食物中毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">首宗個案涉及介乎38至48歲的3名女子，上周五自銅鑼灣黃金廣場的「炑八韓烤」訂購外賣，在辦公室進食約13至26小時後，出現發燒、腹痛、腹瀉和嘔吐等病徵。另一個案則為年齡介乎25至34歲的2男2女，於同日進食購自同一食肆的外賣食物，約9至30小時後亦感相類不適。據</span>悉，受影響人士曾吃奄列及鰻魚，當中5人曾求醫，無須住院，全部病人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心呼籲市民保持個人、食物及環境衛生，預防經由食物傳播的疾病，在外進食時應光顧有牌照的食肆及避免進食生的海產。衛生防護中心已通知食物環境衛生署，並正繼續調查有關事故。<br />\n<br />\n炑八韓烤回應事件，指當日上午11時半，有外賣服務（Plum）員工取餐，當中有超過100份鰻魚奄列蛋包飯。惟炑八韓烤集團跟Plum沒有合作關係，亦不清楚其運送外賣方法及時間。他們表示，至今沒有接獲任何關於該蛋包飯產品的投訴，會配合食安中心指示，並主動停購所有含蛋產品及停用外賣服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b684cc6172676d116cd2cac0af0c4d6c33c4ac88","tid":758398,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180727/s00001/1532697889810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180727%2Fs00001%2F1532697889810&d=Dof9DDvoUSP8Q9BL3XsNpEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=406f8c87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180727%2Fs00001%2F1532697889810&h=af274485\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180727/s00001/1532697889810</a>"},{"pid":"4274777f4c8f601f17fb839253e981a3a042b4ef","tid":758398,"uid":176472,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"炑八 ： 送餐出事，唔關我事<br />\n港鐵 ： 禮頓出事，唔關我事<br />\n鉛水 ： 焊工出事，唔關我事"},{"pid":"de20fbf0020e202cc6a3ef32eaafd188e5103716","tid":758398,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"咁都賴左去plum到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8886f523aa0e542b526fd301a7559db016890d9d","tid":758398,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de20fbf0020e202cc6a3ef32eaafd188e5103716","tid":758398,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"咁都賴左去plum到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鰻魚 疑食物中毒 竟然係關外送事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c72cf687c29b0c330b7a4a9d6607f04316e13ee","tid":758398,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"上次去堂食 <br />\n有fd叫咗曼魚蛋包飯<br />\nd蛋苦既"},{"pid":"956c47dae898ad9585e704e12f7f4e76bf80ffd2","tid":758398,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"嘈到死 想傾下計都唔得"}]}